{"tid":1263354,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益］文宣應該向咩方向走？","createTime":"2019-06-28T06:37:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T13:54:26.000Z","uid":115129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c5ca859f9c63b528324921ba398d7a08a637e9b0","tid":1263354,"uid":115129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:37:34.000Z","msg":"我屋企人係一個自以爲自己好聰明既深藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n長輩圖對佢黎講係免疫<br />\n而佢既思想已經係去到會扭曲事實/常理去支持政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢其中一個諗法係覺得只要示威者唔衝 <br />\n咁警察都唔會暴力對待示威者 佢地都只係執行緊任務<br />\n所以我決定要諗下有咩辦法可以令佢正常返少少<br />\n<br />\n首先 我搜集左一d港台既片段<br />\n話曬港台都係屬於政府<br />\n會比佢地覺得係比較中立<br />\n<br />\n之後我將佢地歸類左5個問題/方面，嘗試決定階段性緊去說服佢（1最易 5最難）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>1+2:究竟點解修例係會影響到佢？</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><ins>點解我地唔信任中國既司法制度？</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n視點31-中國新聞的寒冬(11:34)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Un_hBfkh4ww\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUn_hBfkh4ww&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2Fewiyebd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=260b5518\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Un_hBfkh4ww</a><br />\n<br />\n視點31-中國式陽光司法 (8:40)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vImOEM8LBV8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvImOEM8LBV8&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2Fewiyebd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=c9340de9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vImOEM8LBV8</a><br />\n<br />\n鏗鏘集-活在被消失的恐懼 (21:37)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yaFYM-mgB5c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyaFYM-mgB5c&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2Fewiyebd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=d8b3d266\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yaFYM-mgB5c</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>3:政府並無讓過步 佢只不過係口裏說道歉 但身體很誠實</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n視點31- 撕裂過後如何re-connect （7:05）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Lnrs0RVZeiE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLnrs0RVZeiE&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2Fewiyebd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=bfc99d44\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Lnrs0RVZeiE</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>4.警察使用緊過份既暴力 同警權過大</ins></strong><br />\n視點31-尚待真相大白 <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bA8SueGBYdY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbA8SueGBYdY&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2Fewiyebd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=511f775c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bA8SueGBYdY</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>5.點解我地要企出黎去發聲？</ins></strong><br />\n點解我地有時要衝？<br />\n鏗鏘集-讓聲音聽得見<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zDP6F4evIcY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzDP6F4evIcY&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2Fewiyebd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=71d7fc7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zDP6F4evIcY</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n不如大家都一齊傾下接下落黎既文宣應該點行<br />\n或者有無更加多比較中立既片比佢地睇下？<br />\n同或者講下屋企人深藍既睇法<br />\n集思廣益睇下說唔說服到佢地<br />\n<br />\n利伸：勁少出post 講野1999唔好意思"},{"pid":"da4d85e144d91006c204815a3c2fe338472483ea","tid":1263354,"uid":115129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:54:02.000Z","msg":"1+2:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5nrCZQdMSKQ&amp;list=PLuwJy35eAVaIDgH7hgOpknp7KPOaibNjN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5nrCZQdMSKQ%26list%3DPLuwJy35eAVaIDgH7hgOpknp7KPOaibNjN&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2Fewiyebd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=f700046d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5nrCZQdMSKQ&amp;list=PLuwJy35eAVaIDgH7hgOpknp7KPOaibNjN</a>"},{"pid":"aa905d2f0da4039d0d5a023728f28f122c07dc50","tid":1263354,"uid":115129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:54:26.000Z","msg":"一齊討論下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}